Oh, nice! Looks like you're
making good progress.

rows.label: qst300109_msg002
rows.name:
You know, Mimaira from Sadecott
Groceries said she knew an ingredient
that would be perfect for rations.

rows.label: qst300109_msg003
rows.name: I don't know what it was exactly...

rows.label: qst300109_msg004
rows.name:
Or rather, she wouldn't tell me.
Just laughed and said "You'd never be
able to get your hands on it anyway"!

rows.label: qst300109_msg005
rows.name:
Maybe you should go get the
details out of her yourself.
